00:02:01.948 --> 00:02:04.171
trying to convey the idea of eyes to

00:02:04.210 --> 00:02:06.173
see and ears to hear and a human

00:02:06.212 --> 00:02:06.472
head.

00:02:07.313 --> 00:02:08.675
